high_descs: Walk to your left, turn right and walk along the counter until you reach the spatula.
Pick the spatula up from the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the other side of the room, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Put the spatula in the bowl to the left of the stove.
Pick up the bowl with the spatula in it.
Walk right, then turn left and walk toward the refrigerator, then left and walk toward the white table a the end of the counter.
Put the bowl with the spatula on the white table
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spatula in it on the white table.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the counter, hang a left until you reach the counter to your left.
Pick up the spatula to the right of the black pan on the counter top.
Turn fully around until you are facing the counter top and hang a right towards the stove.
Put the spatula inside the round brown bowl to the left of the stove top.
Pick up the round brown bowl with a spatula inside of it to the left of the stove top.
Turn right until you reach the end of the counter, turn right to cross the room, hang a right when you pass the counter on your right side, and turn left to face the white table.
Place the brown bowl with the spatula in between the loaf of bread and the head of lettuce on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spatula on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the spatula on the counter.
Pick up the metal spatula off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the oven.
Place the spatula handle up in the short wooden bowl that is to the left of the stove.
Pick up the wooden bowl with the spatula in it.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the round white table.
Place the wooden bowl with the spatula in it onto the round white table to the right of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a wooden bowl with a spatula in it on a round table.
